        "subject": "LU-3535 osp: send all of updates for cross-MDT operation",
        "message": "LU-3535 osp: send all of updates for cross-MDT operation\n\nFor recovery purpose, it needs to send the whole updates of one\ncross-MDT operation will be sent to all of MDTs.\n\nThis patch will move update insert to obdclass/dt_update.c, so\nboth OSD/OSP can use api to insert update to the buffer attached\nto thandle.\n\nSigned-off-by: wang di <di.wang@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I51dbf463bca99be5e52ec01ae51a15a9e2a1eaf3\n"
